  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>For breakfast you'll have a hot and cold buffet which runs until 10.30am. Our favourite part of the week is Sunday breakfast where you can treat yourself to smoked salmon and champagne!</p>
<p>For dinner you'll be served a four course Italian evening meal with several choices. The hotel has a great selection of wines which will be the perfect accompaniment to your food. The restaurant has lovely views of the vineyard at the back of the hotel. The dress code in the restaurant is smart casual, so make sure you spruce yourself up before dinner!</p>
<p>The hotel also has a 'Stube' restaurant which is a cosy small dining area, with just four tables, serving up delicious gourmet food (not included in half board, payable locally).</p>]]></cateringDescription>
