  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Villa Nicolli's such a romantic place for a couple's getaway. The Nicolli family have been running the hotel for years and really try to make you feel as welcome as possible. The rooms are fresh and modern with a unique style and the hotel's slightly out of the centre of town so has a really peaceful atmosphere.</p>
<h2>Riva's romantic summer getaway</h2>
<p>The gardens are stunning; having them right on your doorstep means you can nip out for some fresh air or an atmospheric evening stroll whenever you like. The hotel is adults only so you'll be able to relax by the pool or wind down in the spa without too much hustle and bustle going on around you. They've recently renovated the public areas of the hotel so you can enjoy fantastic views of the vineyard from the restaurant where you can end the day with a delicious Italian meal and a bottle of wine from their extensive wine list. Pre-dinner, make sure you head to the bar for an aperitivo, which is filled with light from the giant windows that look out onto the pool and gardens. We look forward to seeing you there!</p>]]></description>
