  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Modern spa facilities</strong></p>
<p>The hotel has a lovely modern spa with:</p>
<ul>
<li>Indoor salt water pool</li>
<li>Sauna</li>
<li>Turkish bath</li>
<li>Salt grotto</li>
<li>Sensory showers</li>
<li>Panoramic relaxation room</li>
<li>Massages and beauty treatments (bookable and payable locally)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Hotel Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Outdoor and indoor pools</li>
<li>Free pool towels available</li>
<li>E-bikes available to rent in resort (payable locally)</li>
<li>Peaceful garden</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Parking Garage (payable locally)</li>
</ul>
<p>Please note, this is an adults only hotel (minimum age 16 years).</p>]]></facilityDescription>
