  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Romantic Twin Rooms </strong>are about 23m² and sleep up to two people. </p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are more spacious at about 30-40m² and sleep up to three people. They have a lounge area.</p>
<p><strong>Romantic Twin Rooms for sole use </strong>are available on request for a supplement, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Tea &amp; coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Shower stall</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>General Information</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The hotel has a separate annexe building 10 metres from the main building, where some of the rooms are located</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A tourist tax of approx. €2.50 per person per day is payable locally</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
